Title: My father&#39;s land
DateModified: '2018-02-24'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/my-father-s-land
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Lenka Arnold
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: "I was conceived in Ibiza/ Spain.\nI raised in Germany with my Czech mom, my\
  \ father is from Argentina and I met him the first time in 2009! In Ibiza! That's\
  \ were I live now.\nIt's beautiful and I'm grateful to have him finally\nafter 28\
  \ years!!!\nHe lives in Brazil, my younger siblings too. I just know them from Facebook.\
  \ \nMy father's sister lives in Argentina.\nI would love to go there, \ndiscover\
  \ the land and the people. \nAnd finally meet the other part of my family.\nThat's\
  \ what I wanna write about! \u2764\uFE0F"
